Package com.topcoder.management.review.data

Class Summary
Comment The Comment class can be considered the third level in the review model hierarchy.
CommentType The CommentType class supports the Comment class, and allows a comment to be tagged as being of a certain type or style.
Item The Item class is the second level in the review model hierarchy.
Review The Review class is the class at the root of the review model hierarchy.
ReviewEditor The ReviewEditor class provides the ability to edit the properties of a review while automatically updating the modification user and modification date whenever a property is edited.
